metadata.name: Hong Kong NEON
metadata.description: They are the adventurers of today; young people brave enough to dive into the unknown and unseen parts of our contemporary cities. They seem to be out of place in this big and hostile space, as if they don't belong here, questioning our relationship with the city as tiny, insignificant inhabitants. But at the same time, they look confident, excited and eager to conquer the world. Lonely in the City but living their life to the fullest.
